des:
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo. After connecting Alexa to your LSC Smart Connect products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our “LSC Smart Connect” app in app market, then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “LSC Smart Connect” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “LSC Smart Connect” skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
